snippet.title: A Creative Open World Sandbox Game Coming to WAX | NFT Game
snippet.description:
LandBox is coming to the WAX Blockchain. Create your own adventure. Play with friends or random people. Get your piece of land to expand the maximum amount of players on your land.

Learn more at https://landboxhub.io
